reviewText: I had no problems watching this movie and I'm happy because I have not seen this movie in years

This movies takes the idea of constructing a time paradox and then explores what might happen, making you sit up and ask yourself, "What if..." and, after all, isn't that what science fiction is all about?  Keeping with a main storyline, it explores various possibilities and different circumstances all at the same time.

for a sci-fi fan even a bad sci-fi movie is better than none. this movie is well done and i like the time travel angle and the stark futuristic landscape.
this movie takes itself seriously and is very watchable.
i felt is was worthy of my collection.

Well its been said that things happen. Thats ever so true in this futuristic time travel thriller. From the moment when it appears that your entire world may have been destroyed by some error in judgement , to the  journey into Time to solve the paradox that will fix this situation. Not to  forget the Love interest.... How to deal with the Paradox versions of Loved  Ones in the other world? I found this to be a somewhat sad and slightly  Haunting movie. I enjoyed it and will watch it many times. The Effects  aren't all that great but the story line is quite good.
